'''''Fallen Leaves & Dead Sparrows''''' is the sixth studio album by Finnish heavy metal band [[Amoral (band)|Amoral]]. It was released by Imperial Cassette in Finland on February 14th, 2014. It was published by G-Regords and released in the rest of Europe on March 28th, 2014, and the United Kingdom edition was published by Graphite Records and released on March 31st, 2014.

"Fallen Leaves & Dead Sparrows" was produced by Ben Varon. Drums were recorded at Sound Supreme studios by Janne Saksa. Guitars, bass, and keyboards were recorded at the home studios of Amoral. Guitars were re-amped at Sonic Pump Studios. Vocals were recorded at Marco's Cockpit by Marco Hietala. The album was mixed by Janne Saksa and mastered by Svante Forsbäck. Arrangements were by Amoral.<ref name="Amoral´s home sites">{{cite web | title=Amoral´s home sites | url=
http://mainpages.amoralweb.com/discography/fallen-leaves-dead-sparrows| accessdate = 2014-04-25}}</ref>

The album has a more progressive metal sound than Amoral's previous 2 albums.<ref name="Interview with Ben Varon">{{cite web | title=Interview with Ben Varon 22.1.2014 | url=http://www.rockbrigade.com.br/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=10791%3Aamoral-exclusive-interview-with-guitarist-and-founding-member-ben-varon&catid=3%3Amaterias&Itemid=7| accessdate = 2014-04-25}}</ref>

"Fallen Leaves & Dead Sparrows" has received predominantly positive reviews from heavy metal magazines and [[webzine]]s around [[Finland]], [[Europe]], and the [[United States]].<ref name="Reviews">{{cite web
 |title=Album reviews 2014 
 |url=http://sites.google.com/site/amoralstreetteam/about-amoral-3/fallen-leaves-dead-sparrows-2014 
